Fana munhu yoyose yonda yahonye chinhu muna yamalagilizo yalaguso ya kitabu chino, Mulungu kezahonya hanhu hake muna yamagongo ya ugima na muna mudibululu da Ukonjelo, viyolongigwe mwii kitabu chino.
Munhu yoyose yogendelela mbuli izo kalonga, "Kweli nokwiza shangu." Amen. keza, Mndewa Yesu.
